2. the freelancer is in an even position##4
3. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
4. the colonial house is in an odd position##4
5. the freelancer is the person watching action movies##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| House      | colonial    | cape-cod   |
